    "name": "Backrooms Society",
    "steam_appid": 2304620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "Make your way through disturbing and eeire levels from the backrooms lore. Each level has unique objectives, optional objectives and resources. Bring whatever you get your hands on back to Traders Keep in The Hub or use your resources to craft new gear and equipment.<br><br><strong>Procedural Generation</strong><br>The Metro brings explorers to random unknown levels with unknown threats. The possibilities are nearly endless.<br>Use your &quot;Journal&quot; to document your findings in these levels. The M.E.G finds great value in accurate documentation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/83f7d09906e403a03a85c331e2effd78.poster.avif?t=1764169257\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/83f7d09906e403a03a85c331e2effd78.webm?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/83f7d09906e403a03a85c331e2effd78.mp4?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Entities</strong><br>There are multiple different entities you can encounter, they're all unique but have one thing in common, they do not make great friends. Beware and listen closely for any noise out of the ordinary. Save your stamina, because you're gonna need every last breath.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/7da4d6f96729fb16023221197152e75a.poster.avif?t=1764169257\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/7da4d6f96729fb16023221197152e75a.webm?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/7da4d6f96729fb16023221197152e75a.mp4?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Defense</strong><br>Some entities have weaknesses you can exploit to make an escape<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/144dfab75c0465392299547a6f5fe0fc.poster.avif?t=1764169257\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/144dfab75c0465392299547a6f5fe0fc.webm?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/144dfab75c0465392299547a6f5fe0fc.mp4?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Immersion</strong><br>Large nonlinear levels with realistic graphics, eerie sounds from unknown sources and proximity voicechat with dynamic reverb will give you an immersive experience to write home about.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/d08decb768afcc93adee1f7f678ba191.poster.avif?t=1764169257\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/d08decb768afcc93adee1f7f678ba191.webm?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/d08decb768afcc93adee1f7f678ba191.mp4?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Co-op</strong><br>Start your journey all alone or with a group of up to 8 players. Help eachother traverse the unknown and gather what you need to strive and survive in the backrooms.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/dc0360e1052e300aa8b9d58d56ecf05a.poster.avif?t=1764169257\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/dc0360e1052e300aa8b9d58d56ecf05a.webm?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/dc0360e1052e300aa8b9d58d56ecf05a.mp4?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Hub</strong><br>The Hub is your safe space, it's a seemingly infinite subterranean highway tunnel, wich has a direct connection to all levels in the form of evenly spaced doors along the walls of the tunnel. The Hub also has a permanently open door leading straight into Traders Keep, where you can trade and get contracts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/8057dccc75ebacccbf92c4842b752a50.poster.avif?t=1764169257\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/8057dccc75ebacccbf92c4842b752a50.webm?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/8057dccc75ebacccbf92c4842b752a50.mp4?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Loot, trade and craft</strong><br>Scavenge each level for resources, valuables and gear. Some loot is level specific. You can use specific resources to craft certain gear to make your time in the backrooms a bit easier. You can make money by selling loot to vendors in Traders Keep and by completing contracts you get from a M.E.G operative, also in Traders Keep.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/7972193d3f92baa90ed8a0374cb0e765.poster.avif?t=1764169257\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/7972193d3f92baa90ed8a0374cb0e765.webm?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/7972193d3f92baa90ed8a0374cb0e765.mp4?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Sanity</strong><br>Entities and other sources can cause your sanity to crumble, keep your sanity high by drinking almond water to withstand enitity attacks and other harmful elements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/4fd06db68ee5968c7c2cffbab9ffbd66.poster.avif?t=1764169257\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/4fd06db68ee5968c7c2cffbab9ffbd66.webm?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304620/extras/4fd06db68ee5968c7c2cffbab9ffbd66.mp4?t=1764169257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
